room_title: Escape room "Organized Chaos" by Room Escapers in Boston
room_description: It’s the early 90s, and organized crime is running rampant in Boston. You and your group of detectives have stumbled upon a short window of opportunity to search a local gang’s front business, Spanky's Pub, for evidence to link them to unsolved crimes. Better hustle though; they’re gathering their cronies, and their lawyer is filing an injunction.
